#: ../../../filesystems/gfs2-glocks.rst:13
msgid ""
"A non-blocking bit lock, GLF_LOCK, which is used to prevent other threads "
"from making calls to the DLM, etc. at the same time. If a thread takes this "
"lock, it must then call run_queue (usually via the workqueue) when it "
